Class Countersignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.asn1.coer.COERSequence
      • org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.ieee1609dot2.datastructs.secureddata.Ieee1609Dot2Data
        • org.certificateservices.custom.c2x.ieee1609dot2.datastructs.secureddata.Countersignature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, COEREncodable, Encodable

    public class Countersignature
extends Ieee1609Dot2Data
    This data structure is used to perform a countersignature over an already-signed SPDU. This is the profile of an Ieee1609Dot2Data containing a signedData. The tbsData within content is composed of a payload containing the hash (extDataHash) of the externally generated, pre-signed SPDU over which the countersignature is performed.
